hs300 = ds.query_index_member('000300.SH', 20151001, 20170101)
hs300_str = ','.join(hs300)
fields = 'pb,pe,share_float_free,net_assets,limit_status'
res, msg = ds.query('lb.secDailyIndicator', fields=fields, filter='symbol=' +
    hs300_str + '&start_date=20160907&end_date=20170907', orderby='trade_date')
assert msg == '0,'
